Module path

Source
Expand description

Every logged entity in Rerun is logged to an EntityPath.

The path is made up out of several EntityPathParts, which are just non-empty strings.

  • EntityPathFilter
    A way to filter a set of EntityPaths.
  • EntityPathHash
    A 64 bit hash of EntityPath with very small risk of collision.
  • EntityPathPart
    The different parts that make up an EntityPath.
  • EntityPathRule
    A single entity path rule.
  • EntityPathSubs
    A set of substitutions for entity paths.
  • ResolvedEntityPathFilter
    An EntityPathFilter with all variables Resolved.
  • ResolvedEntityPathRule
    A path rule with all variables resolved to entity paths.
